Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}[...银色之瞳.]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.73,0:02:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 可以给这孩子系上缎带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子?五百祗先生吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.74,0:02:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 拜托了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 五百祗先生也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.55,0:02:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁高兴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也拜托了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了哦 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么总是带着那种玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是很重要的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃的~好吃的~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轮蛋糕~烤啊烤啊~烤啊烤啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ha~yi~烤啊烤啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林里的熊先生在烤蛋糕~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?真是扫兴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧进来吧 银生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你还来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:04:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想知道 那家伙到底想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要问我 哼 也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们虽然现在是这副尊容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是异界的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还说这个干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底为什么会变成这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天界 人间界 地界还有异界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没意识到其他界存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有人间界的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天界有神统治的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地界有魔王统治的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异界有异主统治的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本原则是互不侵犯各自的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那个白痴五佰祗...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有点白痴的五佰祗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:05:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪那家伙向天界发起战争才搞成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五佰祗向天界发动战争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为那里有他无论如何都想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没有弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学学人家地界魔王的儿子去偷来不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果我们战败了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为破坏原则 那家伙变成了布偶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我变成了熊蛋糕师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家瑞祥被变成只奇怪的鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来神也是忍无可忍了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们虽然也受了牵连
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那家伙作为主谋者受的惩罚最大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做 五佰祗才能回到异界?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那女孩实现愿望以前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五佰祗就会一直是那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也回不了异界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:05:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治愈人类受伤的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当它们装满[瓶]的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩的愿望就会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助那女孩就是五佰祗和神的契约
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙到底在想什么我是搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 有一件事可以肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五佰祗自从到人间界以来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是从和那女孩在一起以来就变了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时不要去打扰他了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先吃了这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.91,0:06:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么好吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的同伴看到我这种样子该哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼先生 在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么来保育园了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找清和有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 吃午饭了 洗洗手进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想今天的会你最好去一趟 就来叫你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己报名参加的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...会是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研讨会 大学里的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大学里的学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次你不是就缺席了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你还是去一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请去吧 藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去不了 我很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 不要紧的 我有个主意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.12,0:08:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午不是有个重要的研讨会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也到这里来帮过几次忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我发现了...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午有午睡的 小鸠也会帮忙的 不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你一直帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 我希望你能认真上好大学的课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真听话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就只肯老实地听清花老师的话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种玩意儿哪戴得下去啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 小鸠 我还会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 请一定要再来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠要连藤本先生的份也一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 弄不下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本那家伙给我绑得那么紧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的是太谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠你在这里真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家以后就好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这缎带很相配呢 和小五百祗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小...五百祗...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 那明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:11:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是有点热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有土的地方会比较凉快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生这里都皱在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道为什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为肚子饿了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个又一个季节过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是为了到保育院帮忙才来这里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天藤本先生不在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想把他那份也一起做了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种话等把你该做的做好再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点装满[瓶]的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的愿望就实现不了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银生?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是五百祗先生的朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 那个要是弄破了我可饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要以那副样子一直留在人间界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄琥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞祥!不要在屋子里飞来飞去!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽毛会飞进面里去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说 可我现在是鸟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个粗暴任性 现在变成布偶的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那个人那里的那个粗人现在一触即发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这点反应?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 拿上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:14:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是给打输一方的慰问品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们绝对会大闹一场哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们之间的恩怨谁也管不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来那家伙就是五佰祗收留的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字也是五佰祗取的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为眼睛的颜色是银色的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是个银色的生物所以叫银生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字确实取得太直白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试过去阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过最后还是打起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被收留还得到了名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他对五佰祗非常执著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有等他们自己做个了结了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那[瓶]交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己来拿不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想就这样被烤熟吗 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的身体怎么可能踩得住我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是身体还是名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么五百祗...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五佰祗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百...祗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是跟你说念五佰祗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五...百...祗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对!五百... 啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比较喜欢现在的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话把[瓶]交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答应我回异界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是跟你说过还有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不回去 直到看着事情结束为止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩对你到底意味着什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我吃了不少苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么抹消她不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个姑娘不存在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 愿望之类的统统化为乌有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该就可以回到异界了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是以前的你应该早就这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子真的是既笨手笨脚又毫无常识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是把自己的事情放在一边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家又没有求她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还累得精疲力尽去帮别人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:18:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不讨厌那家伙的这些不可救药的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人听不下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 里面的东西要挤出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不把[瓶]装满的话就不能实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话只要没有这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想服从于现在的你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银生!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个[瓶]还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有它的话 小鸠就...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从和那女孩在一起以来就变了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说求你了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的你绝对不会说这种话的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点达成目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银生...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生的话好像在樱花公园
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵...来嘛 来抓我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:20:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在和异界的同伴一起快乐地嬉戏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我没有打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在樱花公园吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 真是个不便的身体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过即然到这里了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊 这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生!你在哪里啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您帮我找到五百祗先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.65,0:21:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.73,0:21:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那么喜欢那玩具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我和五百祗先生一直在一起的!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊那家伙还真是挺体贴人的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:21:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你帮我把[瓶]找回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土鸠!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负200分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然让最重要的[瓶]被人抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.14,0:22:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是什么日子啊 谁都要给我系缎带
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.90,0:22:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和五百祗先生一直在一起的!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.37,0:22:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然缎带很适合你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适合个屁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.04,0:22:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再系上一个的话就会更...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.02,0:22:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再系上一个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你住手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.71,0:22:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再系上一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.17,0:22:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 很危险啊

Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.23,0:24:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}[...天使与守护者.]

Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:07.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}人はみな飛んでみたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:15.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}重力に騙されてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:23.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}誰もほんとは飛べるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:32.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あの子があんなに悲しそうなのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.57,0:23:42.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}自分の影をどこかに忘れてきちゃったからかも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:45.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:49.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君に言えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.68,0:23:53.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君が笑えば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:24:00.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いったりきたり　嬉しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:05.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}君が幸せになる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:10.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}心配なんていらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:14.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.94,0:24:27.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しくても涙が出るなんて不思議だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:07.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明明人们都是那么想飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:15.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只不过被重力所欺骗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:23.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}其实谁都可以在天上翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:32.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那个孩子为什么如此悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.57,0:23:42.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}也许是把自己的影子忘在了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:45.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:49.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能对你说 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.68,0:23:53.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能看见你的笑容 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:24:00.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}来来往往中 变得愉悦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:05.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你一定能变得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:10.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不需要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:14.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}因为我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.94,0:24:27.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}喜极而泣总是那么不可思议
